    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your<strong> panko breadcrumbs</strong>,<strong> ground smoked paprika</strong>,<strong> </strong>a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and a generous drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil </strong>in a small bowl – these are your<strong> smoky breadcrumbs</strong></p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
