    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add your <strong>chipotle paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>drained macaroni</strong>,<strong> crème fraîche</strong>, <strong>grated cheese</strong> and<strong> vegetable stock </strong>to the pan</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> chipotle</strong> <strong>mac 'n' cheese</strong></p>",
