    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the <strong>smoky chipotle mac 'n' cheese</strong> from the oven and leave to stand until cooled slightly (this helps the flavours to develop and makes it easier to serve!)</p><p>Serve the <strong>smoky chipotle mac 'n' cheese </strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
